e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T20:54:37.000Z","msg":"去買一大堆哈根大師，問佢攞一大堆乾冰，之後鎖自己係密室，放哂啲乾冰落熱水，一路食雪糕一路等死<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過自乜殺，好事總會發生"},{"pid":"5468cb19b30fdf9660f6f85078db055053f7ec14","tid":1191243,"uid":27664,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T20:55:11.000Z","msg":"當一個人有意去死，就唔會仲有心情去搵咩方法舒服，只會諗咩方法係最快"},{"pid":"822df099097d54cfcf07f0bf96ceb2eb1af81b74","tid":1191243,"uid":249623,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T20:57:05.000Z","msg":"有本舊書《完全自殺手册》可以幫到你。<br />\n不過呢，横又死掂又死，有冇諗下做死士，行弑777呢?"},{"pid":"01bd64a53c23ac977a47ae68d0704292d3fc9c0e","tid":1191243,"uid":181204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T21:00:03.000Z","msg":"去睇醫生，同佢攞抗抑鬱藥，食兩星期之後，開始做吓運動，搵啲興趣班玩吓，識多啲人"},{"pid":"9d42125ff6c008de45e0e3c87a7d5f371717dfb3","tid":1191243,"uid":72030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T21:00:10.000Z","msg":"樓豬話一出街返工已經想返屋企<br />\n返屋企有咩好  出街返工又有咩唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ba66fd3c738f596080806d052fdea872bec703","tid":1191243,"uid":201184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b4a689b05fc88d9a6f5607a3755957b92b52501","tid":1191243,"uid":37537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4e9efb7a5fdda38460636e119398c0d79ccd1e06","tid":1191243,"uid":201184,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"aae48f100dda1ca786b13d517d1123168255c7d6","tid":1191243,"uid":37537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T20:31:46.000Z","msg":"有好多人驚自殺係驚要自殘,驚刀驚針<br />\n如果可以自己打針的話,空氣針/KCl都應該無痛,有啲人話空氣針臨死會痛幾下,因為中風/心臟病咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T20:33:58.000Z","msg":"無讀過書應該會係咁吉唔中血管<br />\n樓豬係咪有咩唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T20:36:15.000Z","msg":"所以果啲人唔算可以自己打針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無唔開心亦無開心<img src=\"/assets